Summary: Describes the properties and member variables of the HingeJoint3D node in Godot Engine.

Property Descriptions
angular_limit/bias (float): The speed with which the rotation across the axis perpendicular to the hinge gets corrected. Default: 0.3.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

angular_limit/enable (bool): If true, the hinges maximum and minimum rotation, defined by angular_limit/lower and angular_limit/upper has effects. Default: false.
  Methods: set_flag(flag: Flag, enabled: bool), get_flag(flag: Flag) -> bool

angular_limit/lower (float): The minimum rotation. Only active if angular_limit/enable is true. Default: -1.5707964.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

angular_limit/relaxation (float): The lower this value, the more the rotation gets slowed down. Default: 1.0.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

angular_limit/softness (float): Deprecated: This property is never set by the engine and is kept for compatibility purposes. Default: 0.9.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

angular_limit/upper (float): The maximum rotation. Only active if angular_limit/enable is true. Default: 1.5707964.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

motor/enable (bool): When activated, a motor turns the hinge. Default: false.
  Methods: set_flag(flag: Flag, enabled: bool), get_flag(flag: Flag) -> bool

motor/max_impulse (float): Maximum acceleration for the motor. Default: 1.0.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

motor/target_velocity (float): Target speed for the motor. Default: 1.0.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float

params/bias (float): The speed with which the two bodies get pulled together when they move in different directions. Default: 0.3.
  Methods: set_param(param: Param, value: float), get_param(param: Param) -> float
